node.detail_zh: 患者由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵，由檢疫中心送院，與第 #1399 宗個案有流行病學關連。（衛生防護中心於 7 月 26 日將患者定性為無病徵的患者。）
node.detail_en: The patient landed in Hong Kong from the Philippines, has no symptoms, and was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre. Her case is epidemiologically related to the case of patient #1399. (On July 26 she was listed as a confirmed asymptomatic case.)
